item.title: CVE-2022-4774|2024-08-03T01:48:40.397Z -- unknown -- bit%20form
item.description: The Bit Form WordPress plugin before 1.9 does not validate the file types uploaded via it's file upload form field, allowing unauthenticated users to upload arbitrary files types such as PHP or HTML files to the server, leading to Remote Code Execution.
